would be leaving.

32:34.250 --> 32:36.000
- Okay, if that's
what'll help you,

32:36.041 --> 32:37.417
I'll do it.

32:37.458 --> 32:38.959
- Thank you.

32:40.417 --> 32:41.917
'Kay.

32:41.959 --> 32:43.417
- Have a good time.
- Wish me luck.

32:43.458 --> 32:46.333
(Preparatory breath)

32:46.375 --> 32:48.041
