37:24.500 --> 37:26.208
- Well, you were right.

37:27.834 --> 37:29.625
- About what?
- Your Matrix thing.

37:32.166 --> 37:35.083
- Well... what was it this time?

37:35.125 --> 37:36.583
- Trains.
- Trains.

37:36.625 --> 37:38.417
- Maglev trains.
- Maglev trains.

37:40.083 --> 37:41.542
- And the best part is...

37:41.583 --> 37:44.417
he turned around
and did it right back to me.

37:44.458 --> 37:47.166
I mean, I've never been
on the receiving end before,
where you...

37:47.208 --> 37:49.250
you just know that
someone is judging you

37:49.291 --> 37:52.625
without even bothering to
find out the whole story and...

37:52.667 --> 37:54.375
I mean, so what
if he likes trains?

37:54.417 --> 37:56.000
Why does that bother me so much?

37:56.041 --> 37:57.917
I thought that I could
just get it, you know?

37:57.959 --> 37:59.709
