38:05.667 --> 38:08.500
- Because you're afraid...

38:08.542 --> 38:10.375
of what, what comes next.

38:11.917 --> 38:14.625
I mean, you wanna meet someone,
right?

38:14.667 --> 38:17.291
You want to fall in love,
but you know the risks
that lead to love.

38:17.750 --> 38:19.542
Oh, they may cause pain.

38:19.583 --> 38:21.667
And it's fear of that pain;

38:21.709 --> 38:23.750
that's what holds you back.

38:23.792 --> 38:27.375
It's what you need to let go of.

38:27.417 --> 38:29.291
- What if I can't?

38:29.333 --> 38:31.709
- Well, that's not the question.

38:31.750 --> 38:33.625
It's not a question of whether
you can

38:33.667 --> 38:36.750
or whether you can't
'cause that's just more...

38:36.792 --> 38:39.709
Taking a risk is like,
uh... jumping off a cliff;

38:39.750 --> 38:42.542
it's a leap into the unknown

38:42.583 --> 38:45.041
with absolutely no guarantees.

38:46.625 --> 38:48.750
Ultimately, Erica,
you just have to decide.

38:50.583 --> 38:53.458
You have to choose -
how are you going to be?

38:53.500 --> 38:55.709
I mean, you could spend
the rest of your life

38:55.750 --> 38:57.500
caught up in that fear. Okay.

39:00.375 --> 39:03.166
Or you could face it,
take the leap.

39:06.250 --> 39:08.083
See what comes.

39:11.750 --> 39:13.625
Your ice cream's melting.

39:13.667 --> 39:15.083
- (Inhales deeply,
exhales forcefully)

39:17.125 --> 39:19.250
Yeah...

39:19.291 --> 39:21.208
I was, uh...
gonna take this to Ethan.

39:22.792 --> 39:24.083
- Yeah, allow me.
(Sharp whistle)

39:25.542 --> 39:27.083
(Tires screech)

39:28.542 --> 39:29.875
- Thanks.

39:32.917 --> 39:34.792
