to this place ♪

39:41.500 --> 39:45.583
♪ Someone hear
my prayer tonight ♪

39:45.625 --> 39:47.750
♪ 'Cause I just wanna do
every little... ♪

39:50.625 --> 39:52.625
- "Chasing the past,
she stumbled into the future."

