going back out on the market,

40:51.291 --> 40:52.583
playing the game in real life,

40:52.625 --> 40:54.834
makes me wanna throw up.

40:54.875 --> 40:57.333
- Ethan.
- Sometimes I wake up
in the morning, alone in bed,

40:57.375 --> 40:59.125
and think, "what if this is it?

41:00.709 --> 41:03.208
What if I never find
someone else?"

41:03.250 --> 41:06.000
I mean, if guys are getting
shot down for having African
mask collections,

41:06.041 --> 41:07.917
it's not looking too good
for me.

41:07.959 --> 41:10.750
- What're you talking about?
You are amazing.

41:10.792 --> 41:13.417
- I'm damaged goods,
and hardly sexy on paper.

41:13.458 --> 41:14.875
An elementary school teacher?

41:14.917 --> 41:16.667
- Uh, your kids write you
fan mail.

41:16.709 --> 41:19.000
- Who still play video games?
- Whoa! I love the Wii.

41:19.041 --> 41:21.208
