Claire used to hate that,

41:21.250 --> 41:23.834
I'd always wake her up.

41:23.875 --> 41:26.375
- (Half laughs)
Do you remember...

41:26.417 --> 41:27.792
when we were roommates
in third year,

41:27.834 --> 41:30.375
and you had the nightmare
about the letters?

41:30.417 --> 41:32.458
- Oh God.

41:32.500 --> 41:34.417
- It was so cute.
It took me like ten minutes

41:34.458 --> 41:35.792
to realize that
you were sleeping.

41:35.834 --> 41:37.709
I had no idea why suddenly...

41:37.750 --> 41:39.750
