and standing in my room.

41:39.792 --> 41:41.291
- Please don't.

41:41.333 --> 41:44.166
- And, I mean, I took you
back to your bed

41:44.208 --> 41:46.834
and I assured you that
everything was gonna be okay;

41:46.875 --> 41:48.542
people were gonna
get their mail.

41:48.583 --> 41:50.583
